OL,6,FA former community first responder has
OL,7,Fmet people whose lives he has saved
OL,8,Fafter his 10-year campaign to install
OL,9,Fmore defibrillators across Yorkshire.
OL,11,FBrian Firth fought the case to fit a
OL,12,Fdefibrillator in near Leeds after
OL,13,Ffinding out there were none within
OL,14,Fseven miles.
OL,16,FTen years ago he had just finished his
OL,17,Fshift when someone had a heart attack
OL,18,Fand died at a local shop, which wasn't
OL,19,Ffitted with a life saving machine.
