OL,3,CMore than 300 defibrillators installed
OL,4,Cacross Yorkshire thanks to campaign
OL,6,FHe has now installed more than 300 in
OL,7,FYorkshire. Altogether he and others
OL,8,Fhave fundraised enough to fit 460
OL,9,Facross the country.
OL,11,FBrain said: "The obvious thought was
OL,12,Fthat if this project saves one life,
OL,13,Fit will have been worth doing, now we
OL,14,Fare up to 23."
OL,16,FThe campaign has gone on to save many
OL,17,Flives, including Trevor Hopton. He was
OL,18,Fout cycling when he collapsed just 20
OL,19,Fyards away from one of the machines.
