OL,6,FTrevor said: "That defibrillator was
OL,7,Fdonated to the cause two weeks before
OL,8,Fmy cardiac arrest.
OL,10,F"It was just incredible that a person
OL,11,Fpassing by was able to get the code,
OL,12,Fget the defibrillator and the doctor
OL,13,Fthat was there, was able to put the
OL,14,Fpads on.
OL,16,F"I understand that on the third shock
OL,17,FI came back to life."
OL,19,FThe campaign has inspired those who
OL,20,Fwere given a second chance to
OL,21,Ffundraise for more.
