OL,6,FCouncillor Ryk Downes was out running
OL,7,Fwhen he had a cardiac arrest. A
OL,8,Fdefibrillator in the local post office
OL,9,Fwas used to save his life.
OL,11,FOnly four months after his Cardiac
OL,12,FArrest Ryk ran the Leeds Half Marathon
OL,13,Fwith the defibrillator that saved his
OL,14,Flife on his back, alongside his wife.
OL,16,FHe said: "If it saved my life, it can
OL,17,Fsave other people's lives, it's about
OL,18,Fgiving back.
OL,20,F"I've fundraised for around seven now."
